title.narrative: Social Safety Nets & Employment Support Project

description.narrative: The Project development objective is to build the Borrower's capacity to institute a transparent, effective and efficient social safety net system through improved effectiveness of non-insurance cash transfers in reaching the eligible poor and disabled; improved efficiency, transparency, and accountability of benefits administration; support of job brokerage services for those who become ineligible to receive cash transfers and are actively seeking employment.
